                <head>143. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On July 21, the National Security Council discussed U.S. policy in mainland
                    Southeast Asia, including extensive consideration of Cambodia. The memorandum of
                    discussion is printed as <ref target="#d64">Document 64</ref>.</p>
